個人（通常有較高的社會地位[來源請求]）和他談戀愛的妄想之中。<br />\n此一症候群的主要症狀在於，患者會有和另一個人（通常有較高社會地位[來源請求]）秘密地談著戀愛的錯覺。<br />\n患者也可能會相信他們錯覺的對象以像是身體姿態、家具擺設和其他宛如無自覺的動作（或若對象是個大眾人物，則通過媒體上）秘止地傳達著他們的愛意。<br />\n患者錯覺的對象一般極少或根本沒有和患者有所接觸，也是患者自己相信其對象和他有著虛構的開展和關係。<br />\n被愛妄想症主要是在妄想症的主要症狀，或思覺失調症的部份症狀中被發現。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4681e26dbb96104fddffd0cb8275fffac48daa","tid":2498021,"uid":297546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"好撚癲，FF到咁"},{"pid":"34c71e9fb894f2db8f9f576b8ffc64d08768cd6f","tid":2498021,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:13:24.000Z","msg":"毒撚唔好ff咁多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我成日都會望住一個方向係度發牛逗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95720d02d3bd445c556c95511a00030ba46d90ce","tid":2498021,"uid":192546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b43ba99525537f46d715773f4eb1a6ae3a74b487","tid":2498021,"uid":1327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:56:26.000Z","msg":"怯夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩黎？叫番懦夫得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係wor打錯添 中文差<br />\nbtw, thx dude!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81066980c5ad5382e5e2e9d70e17f73dc7a17826","tid":2498021,"uid":75487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8433b41254391b5abac54648abb2430a97df2528","tid":2498021,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:10:38.000Z","msg":"咩野叫怯夫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:13:39.0